{"tid":1194880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方：多名戴口罩男子企圖佔領主要幹道並與警推撞","createTime":"2019-06-09T12:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T12:47:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"979597f6b3ae4700583a41268b74afbbf5b60d2d","tid":1194880,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:41:12.000Z","msg":"入夜後，仍大批市民參與民陣發起的反對修訂《逃犯條例》遊行，警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥表示，留意到較早前有人在網上呼籲，前往金鐘一帶集合，計劃佔領主要幹道。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥說，至晚上7時半，有5至6名戴口罩男子，衝出外夏慤道的西行線，企圖佔領有關主要幹道，現場警員曾阻止，遇到反抗，在警告無效後，其中一名警員使用胡椒噴劑，涉及數名男子向金鐘道方向逃去。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥說，警方嚴厲讉責有關行為，對遊行人士及道路使用者造成危險，絕不姑息，強調會嚴肅跟進。他又說，現時政府總部非常擠逼，已經透過主辦單位呼籲在場人士和平有序離開。"},{"pid":"1f52156efde9766636b2061d4126169c4693dac6","tid":1194880,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461734-20190609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461734-20190609.htm&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=a15f7566\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1461734-20190609.htm&h=793db024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1461734-20190609.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b1c6b80c7b23fbbaa4ca813d8a1b5b6890fb87ab","tid":1194880,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:41:59.000Z","msg":"警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2be1ab9c6868085adf0a2306531a6095c74ca8","tid":1194880,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ecf0c60004c18ce7e11bc67f6f47b418f36bdd","tid":1194880,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T12:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class